{"id":692473,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/692473.html","date":"2023-01-30T12:37:39Z","modified":"2023-01-30T12:37:39Z","title":"小晖有感｜围绕胡鑫宇这事，网友们又发现了新的内情","content":"<div style=\"width:42%;float:right;padding-left:20px;\">\n<div class=\"su-spoiler su-spoiler-style-fancy su-spoiler-icon-chevron-circle su-spoiler-closed\" data-scroll-offset=\"0\" data-anchor-in-url=\"no\"><div class=\"su-spoiler-title\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\"><span class=\"su-spoiler-icon\"></span>CDT 档案卡</div><div class=\"su-spoiler-content su-u-clearfix su-u-trim\"><br />\n<strong>标题：</strong>围绕胡鑫宇这事，网友们又发现了新的内情<br />\n<strong>作者：</strong>晖思<br />\n<strong>来源：</strong><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/6X35guhpILIjLYCD2pC1jg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">微信公众号“小晖有感”</a><br />\n<strong>发表日期：</strong>2023.1.30<br />\n<strong>主题归类：</strong><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/tag/胡鑫宇案\" target=\"_blank\">胡鑫宇案</a><br><br />\n<strong>CDS收藏：</strong><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/%E5%85%AC%E6%B0%91%E9%A6%86\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">公民馆</a><br><br />\n<strong>版权说明：</strong>该作品版权归原作者所有。中国数字时代仅对原作进行存档，以对抗中国的网络审查。<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/copyright\">详细版权说明</a>。<br />\n</div></div>\n</div>\n<p>不得不说，现在的网友们是越来越精明了，任何热门的新闻事件，都躲不过他们的火眼金晴，以及缜密思维，再加上强大的搜索工具，于是新闻总能被发现出各种各样的内情。</p>\n<p>这次在胡鑫宇的新闻上也不例外，今天网友们又发现了不少的内情，我想写出来让大家看到。</p>\n<p>今天上午，江西方面的说法又变了，红星新闻说胡鑫宇的遗体是在粮库发现的。</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/01/post-692473-63d7b3e015667.png\" alt=\"imagev\" /></p>\n<p>这是今天媒体报道的原文。</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/01/post-692473-63d7b3e02029b.png\" alt=\"imagev\" /></p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/01/post-692473-63d7b3e02fbf5.png\" alt=\"imagev\" /></p>\n<p>这就是今天媒体报道的粮库位置。</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/01/post-692473-63d7b3e04dcc9.png\" alt=\"imagev\" /></p>\n<p>还借一个网友的嘴，爆出了这样的内情。</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/01/post-692473-63d7b3e05f125.png\" alt=\"imagev\" /></p>\n<p>两易其稿下，最终形成了这样的说法。</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/01/post-692473-63d7b3e06d51f.png\" alt=\"imagev\" /></p>\n<p>在这样的基础上，媒体形成了这样的报道。</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/01/post-692473-63d7b3e07a79b.png\" alt=\"imagev\" /></p>\n<p>结果网友们忍不住调侃道：</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/01/post-692473-63d7b3e086a8b.png\" alt=\"imagev\" /></p>\n<p>有网友则说了这样一句俏皮话。</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/01/post-692473-63d7b3e0915a3.png\" alt=\"imagev\" /></p>\n<p>网友们脑补出了这样的场景。</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/01/post-692473-63d7b3e09cd45.png\" alt=\"imagev\" /></p>\n<p>严谨的网友则摆出了实实在在的证据，这是昨天上饶警方的通告。</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/01/post-692473-63d7b3e0b3191.png\" alt=\"imagev\" /></p>\n<p>昨天媒体也是这么报道的。</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/01/post-692473-63d7b3e0c2ec2.png\" alt=\"imagev\" /></p>\n<p>红星新闻还去实地探访了。</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/01/post-692473-63d7b3e0e7fde.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p>对此，某网友进行了这样的分析。</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/01/post-692473-63d7b3e100dc0.png\" alt=\"imagev\" /></p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/01/post-692473-63d7b3e11340f.png\" alt=\"imagev\" /></p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/01/post-692473-63d7b3e11bc37.png\" alt=\"imagev\" /></p>\n<p>这些也是网友们的分析。</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/01/post-692473-63d7b3e1268b4.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p>有网友忍不住说了这样一句话。</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/01/post-692473-63d7b3e12fa84.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p>也有网友提出了这样一个问题。</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/01/post-692473-63d7b3e13b6fa.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p>有网友则预判到了后面的结论。</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/01/post-692473-63d7b3e14d911.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p>有网友则在11月就提出了自己的预测。</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/01/post-692473-63d7b3e16220b.png\" alt=\"imagev\" /></p>\n<p>网友们对录音笔这事也提出了自己的预判。</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/01/post-692473-63d7b3e16f2cb.png\" alt=\"imagev\" /></p>\n<p>有网友则提出了这样的猜测。</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/01/post-692473-63d7b3e17c3a4.png\" alt=\"imagev\" /></p>\n<p>作为胡鑫宇的同学，则表达了这样的态度，这个我也想让大家看到。</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/01/post-692473-63d7b3e190778.png\" alt=\"imagev\" /></p>\n<p>有网友则在开始给胡鑫宇组CP了。</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/01/post-692473-63d7b3e1a3691.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p>当然，更多的网友继续提出自己的疑问。</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/01/post-692473-63d7b3e1b4349.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p>这些都是网友们的疑问。</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/01/post-692473-63d7b3e1c5499.png\" alt=\"imagev\" /></p>\n<p>网易的网友们则在激辩。</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/01/post-692473-63d7b3e1db16b.png\" alt=\"imagev\" /></p>\n<p>最后有网友一锤定音。</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/01/post-692473-63d7b3e1e9d0f.png\" alt=\"imagev\" /></p>\n<p>这些都是网友们对今天媒体们报道的心声。</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/01/post-692473-63d7b3e209ec0.png\" alt=\"imagev\" /></p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/01/post-692473-63d7b3e219265.png\" alt=\"imagev\" /></p>\n<p>有律师则表达了这样的观点。</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/01/post-692473-63d7b3e22ec27.png\" alt=\"imagev\" /></p>\n<p>有网友则翻出了宋大嘴十天前的发言。</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/01/post-692473-63d7b3e251a8e.png\" alt=\"imagev\" /></p>\n<p>以上就是网友们对今天媒体报道的反应，以及他们所提出的预判，我还是想写出来让大家看到。</p>\n<p>希望在历经重重波折后，最终能有一个让广大网友们信服的答案，也让胡鑫宇能够安心长眠的答案。</p>\n","author":1069,"categories":[45444,45870,41492,43134,45438],"tags":[9369,46442,46445]}